highlights.text: EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “KHÔNG ĐAU NỮA RỒI” is the highest at #8.
“CHILLER” by NCT DREAM is the highest new entry on Top Songs Vietnam at #51.
“Âm Thầm Bên Em” by Sơn Tùng M-TP has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 1674 days straight.
“Em iu” by Andree Right Hand, Wxrdie, Donald Gold, and 2pillz is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 77 spots at #112.
